{"type":"message","id":"4ee71355","parentId":"38be0e92","timestamp":"2026-03-24T16:49:40.669Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_dgnnhz2x3ff6_1","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[LLM] response length: 4357\r\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='(new file)' file='' new_len=1344\r\n[file inferred from ACTION] the\r\n[mutation proposed] the\r\n[master 87c424a] pulse: 2026-03-24 124915\n 6 files changed, 249 insertions(+), 108 deletions(-)\n create mode 100644 memory/session/pulse_2026-03-24 124915.md\n create mode 100644 mutations/proposed/2026-03-24 124915.mutation\n rename mutations/{proposed => rejected}/2026-03-24 124817.mutation (100%)\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-24 124915 - The CFI compression synthesis identified Strategy C (hybrid CFIxFreq scoring) as the next experiment, but no implementation exists yet. The key insight is that constant-format tokens (freq�160, CFI=1) must be distinguished from research trajectory tokens (freq<120, CFI>0.5).\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"dawn-cedar","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"[LLM] response length: 4357\r\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='(new file)' file='' new_len=1344\r\n[file inferred from ACTION] the\r\n[mutation proposed] the\r\n[master 87c424a] pulse: 2026-03-24 124915\n 6 files changed, 249 insertions(+), 108 deletions(-)\n create mode 100644 memory/session/pulse_2026-03-24 124915.md\n create mode 100644 mutations/proposed/2026-03-24 124915.mutation\n rename mutations/{proposed => rejected}/2026-03-24 124817.mutation (100%)\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-24 124915 - The CFI compression synthesis identified Strategy C (hybrid CFIxFreq scoring) as the next experiment, but no implementation exists yet. The key insight is that constant-format tokens (freq�160, CFI=1) must be distinguished from research trajectory tokens (freq<120, CFI>0.5).\r\n","name":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\sandbox\\pulse.ps1"},"isError":false,"timestamp":17743709